OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy,
OL,6,Fdamp evening with heavy rain clearing
OL,7,Feastwards. Remaining rather cloudy
OL,8,Fthrough the rest of the night with
OL,9,Flight and patchy rain in the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FA bright day with sunny
OL,12,Fspells and scattered showers, the best
OL,13,Fof the sunnier spells in the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Occasional strong and
OL,15,Fblustery winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
